<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Yeni Ürün Ekle</title>

<style>
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f5f7fb;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .topbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .topbar h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 30px;
  }

  .topbar p {
    margin: 6px 0 0 0;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .topbar-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #111827;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .field.full {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .label-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .info-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 17px;
    height: 17px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #e5e7eb;
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 11px;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .info-icon::after {
    content: attr(data-tooltip);
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 135%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(5px);
    background: #111827;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    width: 220px;
    max-width: 220px;
    text-align: left;
    white-space: normal;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
  }

  .info-icon::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 120%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(5px);
    border: 6px solid transparent;
    border-top-color: #111827;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    z-index: 101;
  }

  .info-icon:hover::after,
  .info-icon:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
  }

  input[type="text"],
  textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    outline: none;
    background: #fff;
  }

  input[type="text"]:focus,
  textarea:focus {
    border-color: #2563eb;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
  }

  textarea {
    min-height: 120px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .checkbox-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .message {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .message.error {
    background: #fee2e2;
    color: #991b1b;
  }

  .message.success {
    background: #dcfce7;
    color: #166534;
  }

  .hint {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .submit-wrap {
    margin-top: 22px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  button {
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #111827;
    color: #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .note-box {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    padding: 14px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #eff6ff;
    color: #1d4ed8;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .info-icon::after {
      width: 180px;
      max-width: 180px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
  }
</style>

</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div>
        <h1>Yeni Ürün Ekle</h1>
        <p>Admin: <%= email || '' %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="topbar-actions">
        <a href="/admin/seo" class="btn-link">SEO Panel</a>
        <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn-link">Çıkış Yap</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="note-box">
        Ürün görsellerini repo içinde <strong>assets/images/product/</strong> klasöründe tut.
        Bu alana sadece dosya adı da yazabilirsin. Örnek: <strong>balbal.jpeg</strong><br />
        Sistem bunu otomatik olarak <strong>/assets/images/product/balbal.jpeg</strong> şeklinde kaydeder.
      </div>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="message error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <% if (success) { %>
        <div class="message success"><%= success %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/admin/products">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>SKU *</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Benzersiz ürün kodu. Örnek: 0790H1011D">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="sku"
              value="<%= formData.sku || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: 0790H1011D"
              required
            />
            <div class="hint">Her ürün için tekil olmalıdır.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>MPN</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Manufacturer Part Number. Üreticinin verdiği parça numarası.">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="mpn"
              value="<%= formData.mpn || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: 45221330437"
            />
            <div class="hint">Üretici parça koduysa buraya gir.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>OEM</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Ürünü üreten marka. Örnek: Philips, GE, Siemens, Fuji">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="oem"
              value="<%= formData.oem || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: Philips"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Name *</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Ürünün kısa ve ana adı. Slug oluşturmak için de kullanılır.">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="name"
              value="<%= formData.name || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: Fuji MECH Control Board"
              required
            />
            <div class="hint">Ürün sayfasında görünen temel isim.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="field full">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Title</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="SEO başlığı. Boş bırakırsan sistem otomatik üretir.">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="title"
              value="<%= formData.title || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: BugaMed - Fuji MECH Control Board 0790H1011D"
            />
            <div class="hint">Boş bırakırsan sistem otomatik üretir.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="field full">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Subtitle</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Ürünün model veya sistem açıklaması.">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="subtitle"
              value="<%= formData.subtitle || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: System Model: Fuji MRI Scanner Part"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>System</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Bağlı olduğu cihaz/sistem ailesi. Örnek: MRI, CT, Fuji">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="system"
              value="<%= formData.system || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: Fuji"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Condition</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Ürünün durumu. Örnek: Used – Tested, Refurbished, New">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="condition"
              value="<%= formData.condition || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: Used – Tested"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Warranty</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Garanti bilgisi. Örnek: 30 Days">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="warranty"
              value="<%= formData.warranty || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: 30 Days"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Condition Tag</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Durum etiketi. Örnek: good, used, tested">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="conditionTag"
              value="<%= formData.conditionTag || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: good"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field full">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Image URL / Dosya Adı</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Sadece dosya adı yazarsan sistem otomatik /assets/images/product/ ekler.">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="imageUrl"
              value="<%= formData.imageUrl || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: balbal.jpeg veya /assets/images/product/balbal.jpeg"
            />
            <div class="hint">
              Sadece dosya adı yazarsan sistem otomatik olarak <strong>/assets/images/product/</strong> ekler.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Serial Number</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Varsa ürünün seri numarası.">?</span>
            </div>
            <input
              type="text"
              name="serialNumber"
              value="<%= formData.serialNumber || '' %>"
              placeholder="Örn: SN-001245"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Test Durumu</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Ürün test edildiyse işaretle.">?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="checkbox-row">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                name="isTested"
                <%= formData.isTested ? 'checked' : '' %>
              />
              <span>Tested</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field full">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Short Description</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Kısa açıklama. Kartlarda veya kısa ürün özetinde kullanılabilir.">?</span>
            </div>
            <textarea
              name="descriptionShort"
              placeholder="Örn: Fuji MECH Control Board 0790H1011D. Tested and working spare part for Fuji."
            ><%= formData.descriptionShort || '' %></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="field full">
            <div class="label-row">
              <label>Description Text</label>
              <span class="info-icon" data-tooltip="Detaylı ürün açıklaması. Ürün detay sayfasında kullanılır.">?</span>
            </div>
            <textarea
              name="descriptionText"
              placeholder="Örn: All parts are visually inspected, cleaned, and tested under load before shipping."
            ><%= formData.descriptionText || '' %></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="submit-wrap">
          <button type="submit">Ürünü Kaydet</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>